          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Menstrual underwear, period panties, or period pants all refer to the same thing — reusable underwear with built-in protection that replaces pads and tampons. They work during your period, for light leaks, sweat, discharge, and postpartum use.<br/><br/>Sereluna is the first Norwegian brand to design and produce period panties under its own name. Our underwear is safe, breathable, odor-free, leak-proof, comfortable — and looks great too!</p>",
